cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with video prediction. Additionally, the use of autoencoders and recurrent predictors suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of reversible architectures may also suggest a connection to neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the mention of computational efficiency may suggest a connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
